01:46:31,960 --> 01:46:34,070
This duel is over.

837
01:47:09,320 --> 01:47:11,030
Welcome!

838
01:47:11,120 --> 01:47:11,830
Yes

839
01:47:15,440 --> 01:47:16,390
Light!

840
01:47:16,480 --> 01:47:17,150
Yes

841
01:47:17,320 --> 01:47:18,540
Sanosuke!

842
01:47:25,360 --> 01:47:28,750
Maybe the tobacco is making me slow eh?

843
01:47:30,040 --> 01:47:32,500
That one? You're not the one
I want, you messed me up!

844
01:47:32,640 --> 01:47:33,508
The mother fucker!

845
01:47:33,509 --> 01:47:35,150
You're the one blabbering about stinkie!

846
01:47:35,240 --> 01:47:37,350
Where is the legendary "hitokiri"?!

847
01:47:37,600 --> 01:47:39,190
Don't take me so lightly!

848
01:47:40,320 --> 01:47:42,350
If it's to bring him in, I'll lend a hand.

849
01:47:43,320 --> 01:47:45,110
You-Why?

850
01:47:45,560 --> 01:47:48,510
One of your friends rushed to the police.

851
01:47:48,840 --> 01:47:50,110
Yahiko?

852
01:47:53,040 --> 01:47:54,150
Over here!

853
01:47:54,520 --> 01:47:55,470
Look...

854
01:47:58,360 --> 01:48:01,190
A gun like that only works
in one direction.

855
01:48:01,960 --> 01:48:03,830
The other side is the blind spot.

856
01:48:04,520 --> 01:48:06,190
Hey! Come out!

857
01:48:06,320 --> 01:48:09,030
Welcome! Welcome!

858
01:48:09,680 --> 01:48:10,710
What're you doing?!

859
01:48:11,680 --> 01:48:12,550
You've got me!

860
01:48:13,680 --> 01:48:15,030
I surrender!

861
01:48:15,360 --> 01:48:18,070
Hey hey! Don't shoot!

862
01:48:19,520 --> 01:48:22,030
You've already won.

863
01:48:22,360 --> 01:48:23,710
Right, Kenshin?

864
01:48:24,840 --> 01:48:28,380
Just get out here, we can't win.

865
01:48:35,040 --> 01:48:36,550
I surrender.

866
01:48:44,840 --> 01:48:46,590
Put the katana down.

867
01:49:07,960 --> 01:49:10,110
Now apologize,

868
01:49:10,560 --> 01:49:12,590
and bow down to me.

869
01:49:13,960 --> 01:49:17,580
Take them off!
Take off all your clothes!

870
01:49:17,760 --> 01:49:20,790
And bow down to me!

871
01:49:24,320 --> 01:49:25,790
Not in this lifetime!

872
01:49:28,760 --> 01:49:30,270
Damn you!

873
01:49:37,440 --> 01:49:38,420
Shoot me!

874
01:49:38,600 --> 01:49:39,790
Fire fire fire!

875
01:49:41,760 --> 01:49:43,590
Shoot shoot more and more!

876
01:50:03,920 --> 01:50:05,510
Damn you!

877
01:50:18,680 --> 01:50:22,460
Do you know what money can't buy?

878
01:50:32,280 --> 01:50:34,660
What you have now...

879
01:50:42,880 --> 01:50:44,150
Life.

880
01:50:47,680 --> 01:50:48,820
Stop it!

881
01:50:55,400 --> 01:50:59,020
So finally we get to kick your ass!

882
01:51:03,400 --> 01:51:05,830
I'll take it from here.
Go!

883
01:51:09,760 --> 01:51:10,870
Apologies!

884
01:51:28,400 --> 01:51:29,350
Megumi-dono!

885
01:51:32,400 --> 01:51:33,870
Sorry we're late.

886
01:51:34,120 --> 01:51:35,590
It's all right now.

887
01:51:36,400 --> 01:51:38,150
Are you okay?

888
01:51:40,840 --> 01:51:42,710
You must hurry! Kaoru-san is-!

889
01:52:08,960 --> 01:52:10,950
You're finally awake.

890
01:52:18,160 --> 01:52:20,350
You won't break free.

891
01:52:21,520 --> 01:52:24,950
I will use you as a hostage
and it'll make Battousai angry.

892
01:52:25,760 --> 01:52:30,470
He'll be so angry he'll go back
to killing people like before.

893
01:52:41,200 --> 01:52:43,470
He should be arriving any moment now.

894
01:52:56,720 --> 01:52:57,700
Kenshin...

895
01:53:13,000 --> 01:53:14,510
Are you angry?

896
01:53:15,960 --> 01:53:18,830
To involve Kaoru-dono in such matters,

897
01:53:20,720 --> 01:53:24,340
I could not stop myself.

898
01:53:25,720 --> 01:53:26,830
Kenshin?

899
01:53:34,640 --> 01:53:36,710
Excellent, Battousai!

900
01:53:37,960 --> 01:53:39,830
Get angry! Even more!

901
01:53:42,000 --> 01:53:43,140
Kaoru-dono!

902
01:54:09,840 --> 01:54:11,950
Are you going to kill me with that katana?

903
01:54:46,240 --> 01:54:47,220
Kenshin!

904
01:54:49,680 --> 01:54:52,090
Did you not predict that move?

905
01:55:20,920 --> 01:55:21,950
Kenshin!

906
01:55:27,080 --> 01:55:29,190
Not yet!

907
01:55:33,120 --> 01:55:38,030
You still haven't reverted
to the old Battousai.

908
01:55:51,000 --> 01:55:52,110
Kaoru-dono!

909
01:55:52,280 --> 01:55:57,790
A stronger version of Shin No Ippou.
I've paralyzed her lungs.

910
01:56:02,920 --> 01:56:04,800
She has about 2 minutes.

911
01:56:12,000 --> 01:56:13,060
Jin'ei!

912
01:56:14,000 --> 01:56:15,310
There's no time.

913
01:56:16,800 --> 01:56:18,950
Say what you have to say with your sword-!

914
01:56:26,320 --> 01:56:27,790
As expected...

915
01:56:29,640 --> 01:56:31,630
One life is enough!

916
01:56:32,280 --> 01:56:34,710
Don't subject Kaoru-dono
to this, let her go!

917
01:56:35,040 --> 01:56:37,030
It's too late.

918
01:56:38,680 --> 01:56:40,980
There's only two ways...

919
01:56:41,360 --> 01:56:43,190
Kill them.

920
01:56:44,680 --> 01:56:46,670
Or kill the user of the jutsu.

921
01:56:48,800 --> 01:56:50,790
Will you break your vow?

922
01:56:54,720 --> 01:56:55,700
In that case!

923
01:57:47,760 --> 01:57:51,910
Fight me, Himura Battousai!

924
01:58:09,760 --> 01:58:11,270
No more games.

925
01:58:18,440 --> 01:58:21,310
You want me to kill, come at me!

926
01:58:48,630 --> 01:58:51,300
[Hiten Mitsurugi Ryu, Ryu Tsui Sen]

927
01:59:29,040 --> 01:59:32,030
Is this the infamous Battou-jutsu?

928
01:59:58,360 --> 02:00:02,870
Hiten Mitsurugi Ryu,
Battou-jutsu, Sou Ryu Sen.

929
02:00:05,400 --> 02:00:08,230
I broke your elbow joint
and the muscles around it.

930
02:00:09,080 --> 02:00:12,190
You life with the sword is over.

931
02:00:15,880 --> 02:00:16,910
And...

932
02:00:20,560 --> 02:00:22,390
This is the one life,

933
02:00:30,920 --> 02:00:32,830
for the sake of protecting Kaoru-dono.

934
02:00:36,200 --> 02:00:38,550
I once again return to being "hitokiri."

935
02:00:42,080 --> 02:00:43,430
Kill

936
02:00:44,440 --> 02:00:45,270
Die!

937
02:00:46,560 --> 02:00:48,110
Stop Kenshin!

938
02:01:00,400 --> 02:01:02,350
She overcame it.

939
02:01:04,240 --> 02:01:05,460
Kaoru-dono.

940
02:01:08,040 --> 02:01:11,580
Please don't go back
to being a "hitokiri"!

941
02:01:15,320 --> 02:01:17,620
Don't kill him!

942
02:01:22,320 --> 02:01:23,630
You're not supposed to kill!

943
02:01:25,440 --> 02:01:26,470
Kenshin...

944
02:01:31,160 --> 02:01:32,220
Do you...

945
02:01:36,560 --> 02:01:39,310
For those who were killed

946
02:01:43,680 --> 02:01:44,950
Do you...

947
02:01:48,360 --> 02:01:49,500
Until now...

948
02:01:51,480 --> 02:01:53,590
For those you who haved helped

949
02:01:58,920 --> 02:02:00,590
You cannot kill again!

950
02:02:05,160 --> 02:02:08,310
You can help someone else.

951
02:02:10,360 --> 02:02:11,340
Isn't that...

952
02:02:16,440 --> 02:02:17,470
what...

953
02:02:21,720 --> 02:02:27,510
Kenshin aimed for in the new world?

954
02:02:43,640 --> 02:02:45,030
Kaoru-dono...

955
02:02:50,400 --> 02:02:56,230
I'll end this, Battousai.

956
02:03:01,360 --> 02:03:02,580
That's enough.

957
02:03:03,600 --> 02:03:06,710
You have no chance of winning
using only your left hand.

958
02:03:10,240 --> 02:03:12,430
That won't stop me.

959
02:03:23,720 --> 02:03:26,750
It is in human nature to kill.

960
02:03:27,440 --> 02:03:30,980
I may not be talking to the
same person as before...

961
02:03:33,080 --> 02:03:35,540
Murder is murder after all

962
02:03:38,080 --> 02:03:42,190
Can you be a wanderer forever?

963
02:03:43,000 --> 02:03:45,670
I'll see you in the depths of hell.

964
02:04:44,640 --> 02:04:45,830
You do realize...

965
02:04:47,360 --> 02:04:49,095
You won't be able to
bring about justice and

966
02:04:49,096 --> 02:04:50,830
security wandering
around without killing.

967
02:04:51,760 --> 02:04:53,630
Can you?

968
02:04:58,000 --> 02:05:01,190
When one person kills, resentment is born.

969
02:05:02,680 --> 02:05:04,980
Just let people kill themselves.

970
02:05:06,840 --> 02:05:09,190
Until that ideal is severed.

971
02:05:10,880 --> 02:05:14,310
That is the purpose of my sword.

972
02:05:18,840 --> 02:05:21,400
Pretty words, I'll give you that.

973
02:05:33,720 --> 02:05:35,510
Going to wander off again?

974
02:05:39,080 --> 02:05:41,910
The path of rurouni is
an escape for the weak!

975
02:05:48,360 --> 02:05:50,230
Live by the sword die by the sword.

976
02:05:52,880 --> 02:05:55,750
There is no other way for us.

977
02:06:11,560 --> 02:06:14,020
There's a lot of drug trafficking!

978
02:06:14,880 --> 02:06:18,500
Do not miss even one!

979
02:06:26,080 --> 02:06:27,990
Don't let any of this leave the harbor!

980
02:06:28,120 --> 02:06:31,550
These are all very valuable!

981
02:06:36,800 --> 02:06:37,780
I've got money in my pocket!

982
02:06:37,920 --> 02:06:38,950
Money in the pockets!

983
02:06:39,080 --> 02:06:40,590
Gold over here in the pocket

984
02:06:41,760 --> 02:06:43,710
Can you at least grab my shoe?!
it fell off!

985
02:06:43,800 --> 02:06:44,310
Silence!

986
02:06:44,440 --> 02:06:46,590
It's not difficult to walk!

987
02:06:46,760 --> 02:06:49,470
I'll be back, just you wait! I'll be back!

988
02:07:55,840 --> 02:07:56,510
Kenshin!

989
02:07:57,320 --> 02:07:58,350
Oh, you're awake?

990
02:07:59,040 --> 02:08:00,150
Kenshin!

991
02:08:00,800 --> 02:08:01,550
Where's Kenshin?

992
02:08:02,000 --> 02:08:02,870
Huh?

993
02:08:04,360 --> 02:08:06,030
No way!

994
02:08:07,360 --> 02:08:08,310
What is it?

995
02:08:08,560 --> 02:08:10,390
H-Hold on!

996
02:08:19,080 --> 02:08:19,990
Oro?

997
02:08:27,040 --> 02:08:28,070
Kenshin!

998
02:08:28,640 --> 02:08:30,830
You're already up I see, Kaoru-dono.

999
02:08:31,240 --> 02:08:33,470
To the very end!

1000
02:08:33,880 --> 02:08:37,030
A new diet today! Kenshin
was getting groceries.

1001
02:08:37,200 --> 02:08:39,310
Ah! I'm hungry!

1002
02:09:07,360 --> 02:09:10,350
Welcome back, Kenshin...

1003
02:09:16,080 --> 02:09:17,950
I'm back...

